OOC: Yep, Pounce and Wingspan were the Decepticon Clones.  They had identicle 
robot modes, but Pounce was a cat and Wingspan was a bird.  I guess the 
reason for having the same robot mode as someone else is to fool your 
opponenet into thinking you're one person, but your another, with totally 
different skills.
